        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Water Debt Relief Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to implement a residential emergency relief program. Under the program, the EPA must reimburse public water systems for providing forgiveness of the debts and fees of customers who incurred new debts on or after March 1, 2020.</p>]]>
        </text>
